== Troubleshooting ==
The symptoms:
* Missing live video stream;
* In apache logs, couldn't find zms or nph_zms;
  [Tue Oct 27 10:38:55.754977 2015] [cgi:error] [pid 29986] [client 192.168.0.9:54882] AH02811: script not found
  or unable to stat: /var/www/localhost/cgi-bin/nph-zms, .. blah blah
  192.168.0.9 - - [27/Oct/2015:10:38:55 -0700] "GET /cgi-bin/nph-zms?source=event&mode=jpeg&event=5&frame=1&scale
  =50&rate=100&maxfps=30&replay=single&connkey=313914&rand=1445967535  HTTP/1.1" 404 274
* apparent missing socket in the zonemaster logs
  ERR [socket_sendto( /var/run/zm/zms-264615s.sock ) failed: No such file or directory]

* Amendment:

Edit /etc/apache2/vhosts.d/10_zoneminder.conf to reflect:
{{FileBox|filename=/etc/apache2/vhosts.d/10_zoneminder.conf|lang=ini|1=
# ScriptAlias /cgi-bin/zms "/usr/libexec/zoneminder/cgi-bin/zms"
# ScriptAlias /cgi-bin/nph-zms "/usr/libexec/zoneminder/cgi-bin/nph-zms"
ScriptAlias /zm/cgi-bin/ "/usr/libexec/zoneminder/cgi-bin/"}}
in ZoneMinder Web UI change:
  Options -> Paths -> PATH_ZMS = /zm/cgi-bin/zms

To apply changes need reload Apache:
{{RootCmd|service apache2 reload}}
and restart ZoneMinder:
{{RootCmd|service zoneminder restart}}

